otherFacts.name: INTERIOR EXTRAS
otherFacts.value: Double Pane Window, Mini Blinds, Walk In Closets, Thermo Windows, Master Bath, Garage Door Openers

data.description: Immaculate home with tons of updating. 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with renovated kitchen, dining, living room, 3 bedrooms and 1 full  renovated bathroom with in-floor heat on entry level. Lower level boasts a huge conforming master bedroom with egress window, oversized walk-in closet and 5 piece master bathroom. Another family room and the laundry/utility room are downstairs. Both front and backyard are fully landscaped with sprinkler systems for the grass and drip systems for flower planters.
